#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat <<USAGE
Moodle Codex Runner

Core lifecycle:
  ./codex/up [compose-args...]         Start services
  ./codex/down [compose-args...]       Stop services
  ./codex/ps [compose-args...]         Show service status
  ./codex/logs [service...]            Follow docker logs
  ./codex/doctor                        Validate env and docker wiring

Moodle setup and tests:
  ./codex/install [install-args...]
  ./codex/phpunit-init [args...]
  ./codex/phpunit [test/filter...]
  ./codex/behat-init [args...]
  ./codex/behat [args...]

Quality checks:
  ./codex/phpcs <path...>
  ./codex/phpcbf <path...>
  ./codex/changed-files [base-ref]
  ./codex/preflight [paths...]

Container command helpers:
  ./codex/web <command...>             Exec in web service as WEBSERVER_USER
  ./codex/web-root <command...>        Exec in web service as default/root user
  ./codex/mdc <compose-args...>        Raw moodle-docker-compose passthrough
USAGE
